Defendant in custody.   
State moves to delete the penalty enhancer on count 3.   Motion granted.   
Count 3 - Deliver narcotic - No contest plea.   
Count 5 - Felony bail jumping - No contest plea.   Convicted.   Sentences are withheld.   Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for four (4) years.   Conditions of probation are: 
1) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process; 
2) Comply with any other counseling as directed; 
3) Maintain absolute sobriety except for any prescriptions taken in prescribed dosages; 
4) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same; 
5) Comply with all policies and procedures to complete Manitowoc County Drug Court; 
6) Twelve (12) months jail imposed and stayed, to be imposed upon the discretion of the agent and upon order of the Court; 
7) Pay costs of action; 
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC; 
9) Submit DNA sample.    
Minutes.
